{"tid":1019300,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊派利是實況","createTime":"2019-02-13T00:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T04:29:37.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4a77847e55286056bf7a54ab5e5101b2ddaf7e","tid":1019300,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AD4whfICdCIbd3YLwQqu6g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTQwO2g9NDky/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c8b9a436e0a6b5993bdc20841601b81c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAD4whfICdCIbd3YLwQqu6g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTQwO2g9NDky%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc8b9a436e0a6b5993bdc20841601b81c&h=f900f811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新年伊始，騰訊動作連連，一是市傳有份投資的遊戲直播平台鬥魚已秘密申請在美國IPO，二是投資Reddit。<br />\n<br />\n不過今次筆者想分享一下，騰訊的派利是實況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DCEt67fE3fjcGdMhTpCl4A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTk4O2g9NDQ3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/57312f89077408c76a43a4481b877447\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDCEt67fE3fjcGdMhTpCl4A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTk4O2g9NDQ3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F57312f89077408c76a43a4481b877447&h=3d15df5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2QE35b5wYIH2i27evdaOfw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIzO2g9NDY2/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/8586511d45ffd3241d75e42ce6ba91a8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2QE35b5wYIH2i27evdaOfw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjIzO2g9NDY2%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F8586511d45ffd3241d75e42ce6ba91a8&h=85d38d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說逾萬名員工的騰訊今日初八啟市，員工排隊為見馬化騰一面逗利是的場面，可謂非常壯觀，排第一的女員工，甚至早一天就來排隊；傳聞利是幾百蚊人仔超跳，部份更會封上上千元，屈指一算，就算每人封500蚊，派一萬個已經派走500萬人仔。<br />\n<br />\n此外，公司為怕員工著涼，還在現場提供了拖鞋、薑茶及暖包，難怪騰訊的員工，歸屬感會這麼強。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wD1jsi0g3_VGDbOOz5LC.A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Nzg0O2g9NDMw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/7952de6af5f0e7457160923102bbe84e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwD1jsi0g3_VGDbOOz5LC.A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Nzg0O2g9NDMw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F7952de6af5f0e7457160923102bbe84e&h=4b7e66d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bQvrkLC389vmZ_g73yCxjw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NDUw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a94b44cbee6baddbd67dd34aa59ff353\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbQvrkLC389vmZ_g73yCxjw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NDUw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa94b44cbee6baddbd67dd34aa59ff353&h=b07d24ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mKLjLCCipuDTBZ7Ifkhzuw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njg0O2g9Mzc5/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a2074d489dd1ff61f39cb6e6c2f7dca0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmKLjLCCipuDTBZ7Ifkhzuw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njg0O2g9Mzc5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa2074d489dd1ff61f39cb6e6c2f7dca0&h=3f676e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uWl3HJBW6DQBrLztRl3eBg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njc1O2g9Mzc1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/6bcb483b42317b0b6957c77aa424cfd9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuWl3HJBW6DQBrLztRl3eBg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9Njc1O2g9Mzc1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F6bcb483b42317b0b6957c77aa424cfd9&h=b47311a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，筆者最後還是好奇，電子貨幣領頭羊之一的騰訊，為什麼不索性在微信發放全數的電子紅包呢？<br />\n<br />\n來源：gettyimages、深圳大件事等等<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81-084716365.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B3%2581-084716365.html&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=9e4ff150\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81-084716365.html</a>"},{"pid":"93904e23fb37adab6574bccf6abc6723d0bf1c66","tid":1019300,"uid":25002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:06:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"999fda8e695a6596cccb641ae188a0aea6bbb122","tid":1019300,"uid":228143,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"港資 50蚊都唔知有冇<br />\n<br />\n成日話染紅的<br />\n你係員工都識選擇啦<br />\n再好既人才都跳槽啦<br />\nd錢比港資自己賺多d"},{"pid":"06b5a731d760d4518c3f89416b31c3871c7c9743","tid":1019300,"uid":34140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"999fda8e695a6596cccb641ae188a0aea6bbb122","tid":1019300,"uid":228143,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"港資 50蚊都唔知有冇<br />\n<br />\n成日話染紅的<br />\n你係員工都識選擇啦<br />\n再好既人才都跳槽啦<br />\nd錢比港資自己賺多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"20蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b344e0a0265b678d5ca46b5151a45e7646cd76","tid":1019300,"ui